$ System.Text.Encoder (class)
@ System.Text.Encoder

An instance of `System.Text.Encoder` is able to convert sequences of characters into → Windows/PowerShell/language/type/array/byte[byte arrays] that correspond to the converted characters in a given → development/Unicode/character-encoding[encoding].
-
Such an instance should be obtained by calling `GetDecoder` from a class that implements `System.Text.Encoder`.

sa:

 `→ Microsoft/dot-net/namespaces-classes/System/Text/Decoder`.
